'''Am<U+00ED>lcar Augusto Villafuerte Trujillo''' (b. 31 January 1964) is a [[Mexican people|Mexican]] politician affiliated to the [[Ecologist Green Party of Mexico|PVEM]]. As of 2013 he served as Deputy of the [[LXII Legislature of the Mexican Congress]] representing [[Chiapas]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Perfil del legislador|url=http://sil.gobernacion.gob.mx/Librerias/pp_PerfilLegislador.php?SID=&Referencia=9218121|publisher=Legislative Information System|accessdate=14 November 2013}}</ref> 

